  10 Jun 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  -burlap-3.0.8-r1.ebuild:
  Removed old revision.

  10 Jun 2007; Wulf C. Krueger <philantrop@gentoo.org>
  burlap-3.0.8-r2.ebuild:
  Marked stable on amd64 as per bug 179893.

  30 May 2007; Christian Faulhammer <opfer@gentoo.org>
  burlap-3.0.8-r2.ebuild:
  stable x86, bug 179893

  11 Feb 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  -files/build-2.1.12.xml, -burlap-2.1.12-r1.ebuild:
  Move burlap-2.1.12-r1 to the migrated-java overlay because the only thing
  using it is dev-java/spring in that overlay.

  16 Jan 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org> metadata.xml,
  burlap-2.1.12-r1.ebuild, burlap-3.0.8-r1.ebuild, burlap-3.0.8-r2.ebuild:
  Shortened DESCRIPTION by having a longdescription in metadata.xml.

*burlap-3.0.8-r2 (16 Jan 2007)

  16 Jan 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  +files/3.0.8-java5.patch, +burlap-3.0.8-r2.ebuild:
  Added patch to compile with jdks from 1.4 to 1.6. Thanks to Martin Jansa
  <Martin.Jansa@mk.cvut.cz>. Fixes bug #137968.

  05 Dec 2006; Vlastimil Babka <caster@gentoo.org> burlap-3.0.8-r1.ebuild:
  Fix building due to stray space.

  28 Nov 2006; Joshua Nichols <nichoj@gentoo.org> -burlap-2.1.12.ebuild,
  -burlap-3.0.8.ebuild:
  Dropped earlier revision with equivalent keywords.

  28 Nov 2006; Joshua Nichols <nichoj@gentoo.org> burlap-3.0.8-r1.ebuild:
  Stabilized on amd64 (see bug #155622).

  23 Nov 2006; Christian Faulhammer <opfer@gentoo.org>
  burlap-3.0.8-r1.ebuild:
  stable x86, bug #155622

  10 Sep 2006; Joshua Nichols <nichoj@gentoo.org> burlap-2.1.12-r1.ebuild:
  Fixed java-strict errors.

  06 Aug 2006; Joshua Nichols <nichoj@gentoo.org> burlap-3.0.8-r1.ebuild:
  Fixed building with java-strict.

